metadata.name: 3HM #1
metadata.description: Discover 3HM@DTXS, a collection of rare and exquisite Tri-Colored Glazed Horse NFTs inspired by the Tang Dynasty pottery tradition. Each NFT is a masterpiece, featuring unique combinations of background, pedestal, tail, skin, and armor. Only 888 pieces are available for purchase, so don't miss this opportunity to own a piece of history and add 3HM@DTXS to your NFT collection.
